                "type": "text",
                "default": "Understanding Flow State|The Flow State|It's at the **intersection** of skill and challenge. A sense of absolute control. A merging of actions and intent.|It's a mental condition of complete immersion, focus, and enjoyment. Where time seems to stop, and every movement becomes intuitive.|We can help you find your flow.",
